Fondiaria-SAI to Sell New Shares at 1.5 Euros Each in Capital Increase

-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t   a n d   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 
2011-06-23T05:16:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/fondiaria-sai-to-sell-new-shares-at-1-5-euros-each-in-capital-increase.html
Insurer  Fondiaria-SAI SpA (FSA)  approved
final conditions for its planned capital increase, according to
a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  Fondiaria will sell new ordinary shares at 1.5 euros and 1
euro for saving shares.  Investors have an option to buy two new shares for every
one they hold.  Fondiaria shares fell 4.22 percent to 4.45 euros yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  